sources.title: The Love-Stricken | Del Shodegan (1992)
sources.description: The Love-Stricken | Del Shodegan (1992) Synopsis A movie about the Iranian classical musicians in Ghajar era and their struggle to release their first Record which takes them on a journey to France. The Love Stricken Delshodegan Instrueret af Ali Hatami Iran, 1992 Drama, Musical, Historie 91
